Class Coffee

    • sample.MenuItem

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Customizable

    public class Coffee
extends MenuItem
implements Customizable
    An instance of this class is a menu item in an order. This class extends MenuItem class and implements the Customizable interface to provide the behavior of adding and removing the add- ins.

    Prince Rawal, Farah Lubaba Rouf
